第二个版本会加入更多素材提高lora质量和训练更多衣服（校服，黑色骑士团服等）。

The best effect of this lora is the formaldress one , playboy bunny is the second , and the worst is pilotsuitr2.

It took a lot of time to prepare the raw material. But I found that Kallen's birthday is coming up few days ago. So I rushed out the first version of lora before Kallen's birthday.

After the first version of lora, I will train more clothes of Kallen (such as : school uniform, Black Knights,etc) and more materials will be added to improve the quality of lora.
